    "title": "importmulti does not allow watchonly imports while wallet is locked",
    "body": "This differs from behaviour of `importaddress` where it works.\r\n```\r\n$ bitcoin-cli importaddress \"<address>\" \"<label>\" false\r\n```\r\nvs\r\n```\r\n$ bitcoin-cli importmulti '[{ \"scriptPubKey\": { \"address\": \"<address>\" }, \"timestamp\":0, \"label\": \"<label>\", \"watchonly\": true }]' '{ \"rescan\": false }'\r\nerror code: -13\r\nerror message:\r\nError: Please enter the wallet passphrase with walletpassphrase first.\r\n```",
